text: Palmerston North is a city in the North Island of New Zealand. It is the seat of the Manawatū-Whanganui region. The city is north of the capital, Wellington. Palmerston North is the country's seventh-largest city. As of June 2018, the city had an urban population of 86,600. ==Other websites== * Category:Cities in New Zealand Category:Manawatū-Whanganui Category:Palmerston North City
